title: Ex-A&M football player suspected in Dallas jogger killing
text: BING NEWS: Ex-A&M Football Player Suspected in Dallas Jogger Killing Police say former Texas A&M wide receiver Thomas Johnson has admitted to randomly attacking and killing a man on a Dallas jogging trail. Dallas police Deputy Chief Rob Sherwin says Johnson admitted to killing the jogger with a "large-edged weapon" in a ...
